    "body": "Hey @johnjayasingh ! I'm the developer advocate for Truffle - always excited to see developers engaging with the community\r\n\r\nThat being said, I've taken a look at your package and see two problems:\r\n1. Your docs use the Truffle branding, even though we haven't endorsed this project. Can you please remove the logo and name?\r\n2. The linked repo is private, which creates a security concern because it is not publicly auditable. Additionally, it's not in the spirit of open source, which is one of Truffle's core values! Can you please make your repo public?\r\n\r\nIf you are interested in making a more formal contribution, please take a look at our [plugin docs](https://trufflesuite.com/docs/truffle/getting-started/writing-external-scripts.html)! If you're interested, please reach out if you need any help!",
